<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>VestaOS — 民宿运营 AI 操作系统</title>
<meta name="description" content="VestaOS 是为短租运营商打造的 AI 操作系统。VRM 负责收益智能，Cleanfy 负责线下履约。">
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://vestaos.ai/en/">
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh" href="https://vestaos.ai/zh/">
<link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://vestaos.ai/en/">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  :root{
    --near-black:#0B0F1A;
    --surface:#111520;
    --surface2:#161B2B;
    --deep-purple:#540E57;
    --mid-purple:#7C2A67;
    --solar-gold:#F4AD46;
    --vesta-orange:#F18C28;
    --wordmark-gray:#BDC2CC;
    --off-white:#F5F6FA;
    --text-muted:#8A90A0;
    --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --border-hover:rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
  }
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{font-family:'Inter','Noto Sans SC',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;background:var(--near-black);color:var(--wordmark-gray);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}

  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 48px;height:68px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(11,15,26,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(12px)}
  .nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
  .nav-wordmark{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--wordmark-gray)}
  .nav-wordmark span{color:var(--vesta-orange)}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none}
  .nav-links a{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--off-white)}
  .nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px}
  .lang-switch{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .lang-switch a{color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;transition:all 0.2s;letter-spacing:0.03em}
  .lang-switch a:hover{color:var(--off-white);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05)}
  .lang-switch a.active{color:var(--vesta-orange);font-weight:500}
  .lang-divider{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:11px}
  .nav-cta{background:var(--vesta-orange);color:#fff;border:none;padding:9px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity 0.2s}
  .nav-cta:hover{opacity:0.88}

  .hero{padding:100px 48px 80px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center}
  .hero-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(241,140,40,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(241,140,40,0.2);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;color:var(--vesta-orange);letter-spacing:0.08em;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:24px}
  .hero-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--vesta-orange);display:inline-block;animation:pulse 2s infinite}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.3}}
  h1{font-family:'Noto Sans SC','Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:50px;line-height:1.15;color:var(--off-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:20px}
  h1 em{font-style:normal;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--solar-gold),var(--vesta-orange));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
  .hero-sub{font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:460px;margin-bottom:36px}
  .hero-actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--vesta-orange);color:#fff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:7px;border:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}
  .btn-primary:hover{opacity:0.88;transform:translateY(-1px)}
  .btn-secondary{background:transparent;color:var(--wordmark-gray);padding:13px 28px;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid var(--border-hover);font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}
  .btn-secondary:hover{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);color:var(--off-white)}

  .hero-visual{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .hero-visual::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-60px;width:220px;height:220px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(84,14,87,0.45),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
  .dash-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20px}
  .dash-title{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:0.06em}
  .dash-badge{font-size:11px;color:var(--vesta-orange);background:rgba(241,140,40,0.12);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid rgba(241,140,40,0.2)}
  .kpi-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px}
  .kpi{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px}
  .kpi-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:6px}
  .kpi-val{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:var(--off-white);font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif}
  .kpi-val.orange{color:var(--vesta-orange)}
  .kpi-delta{font-size:11px;color:#4ade80;margin-top:3px}
  .activity-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
  .activity-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px}
  .activity-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
  .dot-green{background:#4ade80}
  .dot-orange{background:var(--vesta-orange)}
  .dot-purple{background:var(--mid-purple)}
  .activity-text{font-size:12px;color:var(--wordmark-gray);flex:1}
  .activity-time{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)}

  .stats-strip{border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px 48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:24px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
  .stat-item{text-align:center}
  .stat-num{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:var(--off-white);letter-spacing:-0.02em}
  .stat-num span{color:var(--vesta-orange);font-size:0.6em;font-weight:500}
  .stat-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px}

  .section{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:96px 48px}
  .section-label{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--vesta-orange);margin-bottom:12px;font-weight:500}
  .section-title{font-family:'Noto Sans SC','Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:34px;color:var(--off-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:12px}
  .section-sub{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.8;max-width:540px;margin-bottom:56px}

  .products-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
  .product-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:32px;transition:all 0.25s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer}
  .product-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-hover);transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .product-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--deep-purple),var(--vesta-orange));opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s}
  .product-card:hover::before{opacity:1}
  .product-card.featured{border-color:rgba(241,140,40,0.2);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--surface) 60%,rgba(84,14,87,0.15))}
  .product-card.featured::before{opacity:0.7}
  .product-icon{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px}
  .icon-vrm{background:rgba(241,140,40,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(241,140,40,0.2)}
  .icon-clean{background:rgba(124,42,103,0.2);border:1px solid rgba(124,42,103,0.3)}
  .product-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;background:rgba(241,140,40,0.1);color:var(--vesta-orange);border:1px solid rgba(241,140,40,0.2);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:0.04em}
  .product-tag.purple{background:rgba(124,42,103,0.15);color:#c47fbf;border-color:rgba(124,42,103,0.3)}
  .product-name{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--off-white);margin-bottom:10px}
  .product-desc{font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:22px}
  .product-features{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
  .product-features li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:13px;color:var(--wordmark-gray)}
  .product-features li::before{content:'';width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--vesta-orange);flex-shrink:0}
  .feat-purple::before{background:var(--mid-purple) !important}
  .product-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-top:24px;font-size:13px;color:var(--vesta-orange);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;transition:gap 0.2s;cursor:pointer}
  .product-link:hover{gap:10px}

  .how-section{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .how-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:96px 48px}
  .steps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0;margin-top:52px}
  .step{padding:28px 24px 28px 0;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
  .step:last-child{border-right:none;padding-right:0}
  .step:not(:first-child){padding-left:24px}
  .step-num{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(241,140,40,0.15);line-height:1;margin-bottom:14px}
  .step-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--off-white);margin-bottom:8px}
  .step-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}

  .cta-section{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:96px 48px;text-align:center}
  .cta-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--surface) 0%,rgba(84,14,87,0.2) 50%,var(--surface) 100%);border:1px solid var(--border-hover);border-radius:20px;padding:72px 48px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .cta-box::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-80px;right:-80px;width:260px;height:260px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(244,173,70,0.1),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
  .cta-box h2{font-family:'Noto Sans SC','Montserrat',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:38px;color:var(--off-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:16px}
  .cta-box p{font-size:16px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.7}
  .cta-actions{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}

  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:32px 48px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
  .footer-logo{font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--wordmark-gray);letter-spacing:0.06em}
  .footer-logo span{color:var(--vesta-orange)}
  .footer-copy{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .footer-links{display:flex;gap:24px}
  .footer-links a{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s}
  .footer-links a:hover{color:var(--wordmark-gray)}

  @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  .hero-left{animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease both}
  .hero-visual{animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.15s ease both}

  @media (max-width: 980px){
    .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px;padding:72px 24px 60px}
    h1{font-size:36px}
    .stats-strip{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);padding:28px 24px}
    .section,.how-inner,.cta-section{padding:72px 24px}
    .products-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .steps-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .step{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:24px 0 !important}
    .step:nth-child(2){border-right:none}
    .step:nth-child(odd){padding-right:16px !important}
    .step:nth-child(even){padding-left:16px !important}
    .cta-box{padding:48px 24px}
    .cta-box h2{font-size:28px}
    nav{padding:0 20px}
    .nav-links{display:none}
    footer{padding:24px;flex-direction:column;text-align:center}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="/zh/" class="nav-logo">
    <svg width="38" height="24" viewBox="0 0 48 30" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M10 15 C10 8,18 4,24 8 C30 4,38 8,38 15 C38 22,30 26,24 22 C18 26,10 22,10 15Z" stroke="url(#gs)" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <circle cx="24" cy="15" r="3.5" fill="url(#go)"/>
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="gs" x1="10" y1="15" x2="38" y2="15" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#540E57"/>
          <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#F4AD46"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7C2A67"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="go" x1="20" y1="11" x2="28" y2="19" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F4AD46"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F18C28"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
    </svg>
    <span class="nav-wordmark">VESTA <span>OS</span></span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#products">产品</a></li>
    <li><a href="#how">运行原理</a></li>
    <li><a href="#partners">城市合作</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">关于我们</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <div class="lang-switch">
      <a href="/en/">EN</a>
      <span class="lang-divider">|</span>
      <a href="/zh/" class="active">中</a>
    </div>
    <button class="nav-cta">申请演示</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">AI 民宿运营操作系统</div>
    <h1>规模化运营，<br><em>从未如此轻松</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">VestaOS 是专为短租运营商打造的 AI 操作系统。VRM 负责智能定价与收益优化，Cleanfy 负责线下履约执行——两个引擎，一个闭环。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <button class="btn-primary">免费开始使用</button>
      <button class="btn-secondary">观看演示 →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="dash-header">
      <span class="dash-title">VestaOS · 实时看板</span>
      <span class="dash-badge">● 实时同步</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-row">
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="kpi-label">管理房源</div>
        <div class="kpi-val orange">990+</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta">↑ 3.5x 同比</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="kpi-label">本月收入</div>
        <div class="kpi-val">$4.55M</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta">↑ 18% 环比</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div class="kpi-label">毛利率</div>
        <div class="kpi-val">89%</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta">软件层</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-list">
      <div class="activity-item">
        <div class="activity-dot dot-green"></div>
        <span class="activity-text">VRM 已更新 #LA-0412 动态定价 +12%</span>
        <span class="activity-time">刚刚</span>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-item">
        <div class="activity-dot dot-orange"></div>
        <span class="activity-text">Cleanfy 调度清洁员 · 3号公寓 → 08:30</span>
        <span class="activity-time">2分钟前</span>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-item">
        <div class="activity-dot dot-purple"></div>
        <span class="activity-text">AI 客服已自动回复 · 满意度 98%</span>
        <span class="activity-time">5分钟前</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-strip">
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-num">990<span>+</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">管理房源总数</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-num">3<span> 座城市</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">温哥华 · 洛杉矶 · 芝加哥</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-num">89<span>%</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">软件层毛利率</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <div class="stat-num">12.4<span>x</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">LTV / CAC 比</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="products">
  <div class="section-label">两大核心产品</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">AI 大脑 + 落地执行</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">VestaOS 将智能决策与线下执行融为一体，彻底打通运营闭环——这是分散工具永远做不到的。</p>
  <div class="products-grid">
    <article class="product-card featured">
      <div class="product-icon icon-vrm">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
          <path d="M3 17l5-5 4 4 9-9" stroke="#F18C28" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M21 8h-5V3" stroke="#F18C28" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span class="product-tag">AI 定价引擎</span>
      <h3 class="product-name">VRM</h3>
      <p class="product-desc">基于市场数据、竞对分析与历史表现，实时自动调整定价策略。AI 驱动的收益管理，让每一间夜都实现最优定价。</p>
      <ul class="product-features">
        <li>多平台动态定价（Airbnb、VRBO、直销）</li>
        <li>AI 供需预测与收益优化</li>
        <li>实时竞对监控与自动响应</li>
        <li>GraphQL API · 无缝对接 PMS</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#" class="product-link">了解 VRM →</a>
    </article>
    <article class="product-card">
      <div class="product-icon icon-clean">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
          <path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2" stroke="#c47fbf" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="4" rx="1" stroke="#c47fbf" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="#c47fbf" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span class="product-tag purple">线下履约网络</span>
      <h3 class="product-name">Cleanfy</h3>
      <p class="product-desc">城市级清洁调度与履约网络。退房自动派单、GPS 实时追踪、AI 照片质检——让每一次房间交接都无缝衔接。</p>
      <ul class="product-features">
        <li class="feat-purple">退房触发自动派单</li>
        <li class="feat-purple">清洁员 GPS 实时追踪</li>
        <li class="feat-purple">AI 照片质检与自动验收</li>
        <li class="feat-purple">自动结算 · 35% 佣金模式</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#" class="product-link" style="color:#c47fbf">了解 Cleanfy →</a>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="how-inner">
    <div class="section-label">运营闭环</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">四步，全自动</h2>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">VRM 智能定价</div>
        <div class="step-desc">AI 实时分析市场，每天自动更新各平台价格，无需人工干预。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">AI 客服 7×24</div>
